Package: DESandbox
Type: Package
Title: Unified Interface for Differential Expression Analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeongah", "Lee", email = "jeongahblair@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides a unified interface for running and comparing differential 
    expression analyses using DESeq2, edgeR, and limma-voom. Standardizes outputs,
    enables cross-method comparison, and integrates gene set enrichment analysis.
    Designed for reproducibility and API integration.
